  "help_introduction_header": "Game Instructions",
  "help_introduction_description_0": "The goal of the game is to select 2–6 cards that you believe are included among the 12 cards drawn by the game.",
  "help_introduction_description_1": "The game uses two decks of cards without jokers.",
  "help_introduction_description_2": "The first deck contains 52 cards, from which you select 2–6 lucky cards.",
  "help_introduction_description_3": "The second deck contains 53 cards, including the Dragon Card. This deck is used in the draw so that in the base game, the Dragon Card is included, while it is excluded from free games and the gamble feature.",
  "help_how_to_play_header": "How to play",
  "help_how_to_play_description_0": "• Press BET button to select the desired bet for the round.",
  "help_how_to_play_description_1": "• Choose 2–6 lucky cards by tapping them on the screen. You can deselect a card by tapping on it again. The CANCEL button removes all card selections.",
  "help_how_to_play_description_2": "• The QUICK PLAY button automatically selects random cards for you. If you’ve selected 0–1 cards, pressing the QUICK PLAY button fills the selection to six cards. If you’ve selected 2–6 cards, pressing QUICK PLAY replaces your selected cards with an equal number of new random cards.",
  "help_how_to_play_description_3": "• Press PLAY button to start the round.",
  "help_card_deck_header": "Deck of cards",
  "help_card_deck_description_0": "The game uses a deck of 52 cards.",
  "help_card_deck_description_1": "The card values are:",
  "help_card_deck_description_2": "- King (K): 13",
  "help_card_deck_description_3": "- Queen (Q): 12",
  "help_card_deck_description_4": "- Jack (J): 11",
  "help_card_deck_description_5": "- 2-10: Numerical value",
  "help_card_deck_description_6": "- Ace (A): 1",
  "help_dragon_card_header": "Dragon Card",
  "help_dragon_card_description_0": "At the start of each round, the dragon panel displays either a random multiplier or a free games symbol.",
  "help_dragon_card_description_1": "If the Dragon Card is among the drawn cards, the multiplier is applied to the round’s winnings, or the player wins three free games.",
  "help_dragon_card_description_2": "In the base game, the multiplier can be 2x, 3x, 5x, 7x, 10x, 50x, or 100x.",
  "help_freespins_header": "Free rounds",
  "help_freespins_description_0": "If the dragon panel displays a free game symbol and the Dragon Card is among the drawn cards, the player wins 3 free games.",
  "help_freespins_description_1": "Free games are played with the same bet as the round in which they were won.",
  "help_freespins_description_2": "In free games, 4 cards are selected.",
  "help_freespins_description_3": "Before each free game, a random multiplier is drawn for that round. In free games, the multiplier can be 2x, 3x, 5x, 10x, 15x, 25x, 50x, or 100x. The multiplier is active on every free game round.",
  "help_freespins_description_4": "Free games cannot trigger additional free games.",
  "help_freespins_description_5": "The Dragon Card is not included in free games.",
  "help_gamble_header": "Gamble",
  "help_gamble_description_0": "In the gamble feature, you are dealt five cards, with the first card on the left facing up (the displayed card).",
  "help_gamble_description_1": "Choose one of the four remaining cards (selected card).",
  "help_gamble_description_2": "If the selected card has a higher value than the displayed card, you double your winnings. You can continue gambling by pressing GAMBLE or stop and collect your winnings by pressing COLLECT.",
  "help_gamble_description_3": "If the selected card has a lower value than the displayed card, you lose the gambled amount, and the gamble feature ends.",
  "help_gamble_description_4_tie_win": "If the selected card has the same value as the displayed card, the gambled bet is paid back. You can continue by pressing GAMBLE or collect by pressing COLLECT.",
  "help_gamble_description_4_tie_break": "If the selected card has the same value as the displayed card, the outcome of the gamble depends on the color of the displayed card:",
  "help_gamble_description_4_tie_break_red": "If the displayed card is red, the gambled bet is paid back. You can continue by pressing GAMBLE or collect by pressing COLLECT.",
  "help_gamble_description_4_tie_break_black": "If the displayed card is black, you lose the gambled amount, and the feature ends.",
  "help_gamble_description_5": "The Dragon Card is not included in the gamble feature, and the Ace has a value of 1.",
  "help_gamble_description_6": "The maximum win from the Gamble feature is limited to the game's maximum win multiplier.",
  "help_wins_header": "Winnings",
  "help_wins_description_0": "The paytable displays the number of winning hits and the payout amounts.",
  "help_wins_description_1": "Transfer your winnings to your balance by pressing COLLECT or try to increase your winnings with the gamble feature by pressing GAMBLE.",
  "help_wins_description_2": "The maximum win multiplier per game round (base game + any free spins) is {maxWinFactor} times the total bet. If the win for a game round reaches this limit, the game round ends immediately, and any remaining free spins will not be played. The player is awarded a win according to the maximum win multiplier.",
  "intro_dragon_card_header": "DRAGON CARD",
  "intro_dragon_card_text": "The Dragon triggers free spins, or activates a random multiplier for the round, up to 100x!",
  "intro_freespin_header": "FREE ROUNDS",
  "intro_freespin_text": "Three free rounds - with four cards of your choice. Each round has an active win multiplier!",
